benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: DELETE /1.0/kb/admin/cache/tenants - Invalidates Caches per tenant level

covered: Non-Existent Resource: 404 when tenant not found (TC04).
Server Error Handling: 500 and 503 error scenarios (TC05, TC06).
Bad Request: 400 for malformed/extra parameters (TC07, TC08).
Edge Case/Idempotency: Idempotent behavior when cache already empty (TC09).
Integration/Dependent Services: Cache invalidation reflected in dependents (TC12).
Regression: Previously fixed error does not recur (TC11).
Security Testing: Injection attempt in headers covered (TC08).
Performance under load: Multiple concurrent requests and timing (TC10).
gaps: Caching Behavior: No testing of HTTP caching headers (ETag/Cache-Control).
Pagination: Not applicable or not tested for large datasets.
Rate Limiting: No tests for throttling or rate limiting.
403 Forbidden Coverage: Tests only cover 401; explicit 403 not tested.
recommendations: Add tests to verify caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control).
Add pagination tests if tenant caches can grow large; otherwise document as not applicable.
Add tests to cover 403 Forbidden responses in addition to 401.
